sanuwave-client (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Qt6-based medical imaging client
  * Multi-camera streaming support (RGB, thermal)
  * TurboJPEG hardware-accelerated decoding
  * COLMAP integration for 3D reconstruction
  * Wound measurement and analysis tools

